data.horoscope_data: Get ready for your values to change over the next couple of months now that Neptune has briefly left your sign for Aries. You might realize that your deeply held beliefs and personal tastes can easily shift. Invest in whatever brings meaning to your life, Pisces.Fake it till you make it when Mars in Cancer trines Saturn in your sign on Friday. Making time for personal pleasure can be just the boost you need to move forward. You can’t run on empty without having some kind of treat.End the week on a romantic note when Venus in your sign trines Mars on Sunday. It’s easy to fall head over heels today, even if it’s with someone you’ve known for a long time. This is a great night to go on a unique date or enjoy a spring fling with someone you care about.
